{
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 0,
          "dDurationMs": 7000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Transcriber: Ánh Minh Nguyễn Reviewer: TO NGUYEN MONG LANH� DCVX"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 10196,
          "dDurationMs": 6280,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Have you ever walked into a room and thought, I do not fit in here?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 17596,
          "dDurationMs": 2000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I'm feeling that way right now."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 20556,
          "dDurationMs": 5040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "To American for the British, to British, for the Americans."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 26316,
          "dDurationMs": 6720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "As humans, we have this almost visceral need to belong."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 33676,
          "dDurationMs": 6680,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "This craving to feel safe and included in our in-group of humans."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 40636,
          "dDurationMs": 5440,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "No one gets through life without feeling like an outsider."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 47156,
          "dDurationMs": 4960,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But instead of allowing these natural feelings of exclusion"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 52116,
          "dDurationMs": 2200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "and rejection to stop us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 55556,
          "dDurationMs": 4120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "What if we turned them into an opportunity"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 59676,
          "dDurationMs": 3240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "to make a real difference in the world."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 66156,
          "dDurationMs": 4560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "You may or may not have heard about this dye stuff."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 71556,
          "dDurationMs": 5680,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "In simple terms, dye stands for diversity, equity,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 77636,
          "dDurationMs": 1200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "and inclusion."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 80156,
          "dDurationMs": 1960,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It was meant to be a good thing,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 82716,
          "dDurationMs": 2760,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "but the way some people talk about it right now,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 85476,
          "dDurationMs": 4120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "you might think it's the worst thing ever."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 91116,
          "dDurationMs": 4280,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "The problem is we've gotten dye backwards."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 96356,
          "dDurationMs": 2840,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It should actually be I'd."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 100636,
          "dDurationMs": 2960,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "And I don't mean the thing that goes boom."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 106036,
          "dDurationMs": 6000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Although the current dye conversation certainly seems explosive."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 112996,
          "dDurationMs": 3040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "The problem with our almost obsession"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 116356,
          "dDurationMs": 6200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "with diversity is that it's just the bean counting of difference."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 122796,
          "dDurationMs": 2800,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "How many of these types of people do we have?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 125876,
          "dDurationMs": 3040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "How many of those types of people do we have?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 130236,
          "dDurationMs": 4760,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But it's not the thing that's going to make a real difference."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 135996,
          "dDurationMs": 3520,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "That's why we need to focus on inclusion."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 140316,
          "dDurationMs": 5560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Because if we focus on inclusion, equity and diversity will come."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 146556,
          "dDurationMs": 6200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I mean, who doesn't want to live in a fairer world with real opportunity"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 152796,
          "dDurationMs": 1000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "for all?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 155116,
          "dDurationMs": 6640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "If, like me, you care about Dei, you might be really worried right now."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 162796,
          "dDurationMs": 1720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Laws are being rolled back."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 164996,
          "dDurationMs": 5560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "1 in 8 US companies eliminated or reduced Dei programs in 2024,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 171076,
          "dDurationMs": 1640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "with more cuts coming."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 174556,
          "dDurationMs": 5920,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "56% of hiring managers say die just for PR,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 180796,
          "dDurationMs": 6120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "not real change."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 186916,
          "dDurationMs": 6240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "and woke is being used as a political weapon on both sides of the Atlantic."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 194276,
          "dDurationMs": 1800,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Pretty bleak, isn't it?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 196556,
          "dDurationMs": 5080,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But in the next ten minutes, I'll show you how you can keep Dei moving forward."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 203116,
          "dDurationMs": 2160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Let's take a tour of history."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 205556,
          "dDurationMs": 4640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "For centuries, people have dominated one another."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 210356,
          "dDurationMs": 4480,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Think alpha males, Genghis Khan, silverback gorillas,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 215796,
          "dDurationMs": 4800,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "the dominated rise and become the new dominators."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 220796,
          "dDurationMs": 3240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Cycles like these have always existed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 224036,
          "dDurationMs": 2400,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Imbalances. Unfairness."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 226676,
          "dDurationMs": 1720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "In-group power dynamics."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 229956,
          "dDurationMs": 6560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But set aside history for a moment and consider your own family story."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 236836,
          "dDurationMs": 5280,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Was there a time when you or your relatives were less powerful"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 242316,
          "dDurationMs": 3160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "or excluded from the dominant group?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 246356,
          "dDurationMs": 6200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "How did that shape your life and your feelings of self-worth and belonging?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 253796,
          "dDurationMs": 5760,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Most of us can relate to being on the losing side at some point."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 259916,
          "dDurationMs": 3680,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We suppress those memories, try to rise above them."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 264196,
          "dDurationMs": 6040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But how often do we consider that we might have become part"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 270236,
          "dDurationMs": 6160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "of the dominant group, sometimes without even noticing?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 277236,
          "dDurationMs": 2040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Sit with that discomfort."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 279516,
          "dDurationMs": 5000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We'll return to it. History shows that Di progress"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 284516,
          "dDurationMs": 3880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "and backlash are cyclical in the 18th century."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 288436,
          "dDurationMs": 2640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Abolition and women's rights movements began."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 292116,
          "dDurationMs": 6080,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But by the 19th century, slavery, patriarchy and exclusion fought back hard."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 298956,
          "dDurationMs": 5200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "In the late 19th century, slavery was abolished and some suffrage gained."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 305156,
          "dDurationMs": 2720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Yet apartheid and segregation laws,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 307916,
          "dDurationMs": 5880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "racial violence and misogyny took root in the 20th century."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 313836,
          "dDurationMs": 6240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "White women and black women won the vote, and black institutions grew."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 321076,
          "dDurationMs": 4000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But discrimination and segregation kept progress slow."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 326356,
          "dDurationMs": 4920,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "The 1960s and 70s saw landmark civil rights laws enacted,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 331956,
          "dDurationMs": 4120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "but were also met with fierce resistance and rollbacks."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 336836,
          "dDurationMs": 6600,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It can feel like a yo yo progress, then regression."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 343676,
          "dDurationMs": 2560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But overall we move forward."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 348036,
          "dDurationMs": 3680,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "So where are we in the current D II cycle?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 352156,
          "dDurationMs": 4160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "And why does it feel like we're going backwards right now?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 357596,
          "dDurationMs": 4080,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "According to social scientists like Pitirim Sorokin and Oswald Spengler,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 362156,
          "dDurationMs": 4200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "they noticed that history moves in waves."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 366756,
          "dDurationMs": 3240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Periods of progress then push back."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 370196,
          "dDurationMs": 4240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Every big step towards equality triggers a resistance from the people"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 374436,
          "dDurationMs": 2240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "and structures defending the status quo."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 378676,
          "dDurationMs": 5440,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "After the financial crisis of 2008, our world entered a new era."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 384876,
          "dDurationMs": 6200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Institutions weakened, political divides grew, and society polarized."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 391516,
          "dDurationMs": 4560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Movements like Me Too and Black Lives Matter rose to prominence,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 396276,
          "dDurationMs": 4040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "but were also met with fierce backlash and resistance."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 400796,
          "dDurationMs": 5960,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It can feel like the pendulum keeps swinging back."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 407316,
          "dDurationMs": 2960,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But cycles like these are normal."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 410316,
          "dDurationMs": 4120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "They're how societies adapt and eventually grow stronger."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 416156,
          "dDurationMs": 1680,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It's tough to hear,"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 419196,
          "dDurationMs": 5280,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "but things might get worse before they get better."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 426476,
          "dDurationMs": 4560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Backlash is simply a natural part of social change."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 431316,
          "dDurationMs": 5160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It can come from oppressed groups pushing back against their oppression"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 436876,
          "dDurationMs": 3080,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "or from those resisting change."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 441516,
          "dDurationMs": 4480,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Most of us can relate to being oppressed"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 446356,
          "dDurationMs": 3920,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "or excluded from the dominant group."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 451036,
          "dDurationMs": 4880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We like to think of ourselves as the good ones."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 456716,
          "dDurationMs": 3720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We're on the right side of history."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 461956,
          "dDurationMs": 2640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "But if we're being honest,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 465236,
          "dDurationMs": 5200,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "are we sometimes the ones holding privilege and power over others?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 472276,
          "dDurationMs": 3520,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I wonder if you see that in yourself."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 476196,
          "dDurationMs": 1320,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I know I do."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 478756,
          "dDurationMs": 2320,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "As a woman, I face discrimination."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 481516,
          "dDurationMs": 4680,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Yet as a white person, I hold privilege and power over others,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 486516,
          "dDurationMs": 3080,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "even if I never intended it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 490276,
          "dDurationMs": 2320,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "That's how society works."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 492876,
          "dDurationMs": 2120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It shapes us. And just"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 494996,
          "dDurationMs": 4480,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "because you're advocating for Dei doesn't make you immune."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 500116,
          "dDurationMs": 4760,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We all have unconscious bias without realizing it."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 506356,
          "dDurationMs": 2640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I used to think that I was one"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 508996,
          "dDurationMs": 3720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "of the good Dei champions"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 513916,
          "dDurationMs": 5120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "until 15 years ago. I changed careers"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 519956,
          "dDurationMs": 3400,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "after over a decade of working on Wall Street,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 523356,
          "dDurationMs": 3120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I joined a fast growing restaurant group."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 526916,
          "dDurationMs": 4000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "It felt like a promotion and a chance to be myself."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 531036,
          "dDurationMs": 3520,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Ditch the power suits and make a real difference."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 535156,
          "dDurationMs": 6760,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Shortly after I joined the company, my boss who hired me left his replacement."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 542276,
          "dDurationMs": 4440,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Let's call him Aiden was tough,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 547636,
          "dDurationMs": 6640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "proud of being a rough and tumble type and from the wrong side of Dublin."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 555156,
          "dDurationMs": 2800,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "He was a bully and he told us so."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 558516,
          "dDurationMs": 5760,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "As I had the unpleasant task of making Aiden successful in his new role,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 564956,
          "dDurationMs": 7000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I did what any other self-respecting human resource professional would do."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 573276,
          "dDurationMs": 5240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "I did exactly what Aiden told me to do."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 579676,
          "dDurationMs": 3120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Aiden gave me a list of problem people,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 582956,
          "dDurationMs": 3480,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "people he wanted gone from the business."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 586796,
          "dDurationMs": 6440,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "So I worked my way through the list and one by one I fired close to 20 people."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 594516,
          "dDurationMs": 6040,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Months later, I was looking around the senior leadership table"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 601196,
          "dDurationMs": 5160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "and I realized only one woman was left."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 609156,
          "dDurationMs": 1000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Me."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 611596,
          "dDurationMs": 6440,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Without noticing, I had fired all of the other senior women."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 619756,
          "dDurationMs": 5640,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "If I can do that unconsciously to other women,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 626436,
          "dDurationMs": 6160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "what might I be doing or ignoring with people who are trans,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 632876,
          "dDurationMs": 4280,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "non-binary, gay, neurodiverse,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 637196,
          "dDurationMs": 3520,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "people of color, or disabled."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 641796,
          "dDurationMs": 3880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We are all part of the problem,"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 646876,
          "dDurationMs": 4840,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "but we are all also part of the solution."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 652956,
          "dDurationMs": 4960,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "We all have unconscious bias that's stopping die progress."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 657916,
          "dDurationMs": 3920,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "So what do you do? Especially if you care about fairness."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 661876,
          "dDurationMs": 5280,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Inclusion. First of all, do not give up."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 668676,
          "dDurationMs": 1920,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Be in action."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 672396,
          "dDurationMs": 1800,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Second of all, observe,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 674196,
          "dDurationMs": 5560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "monitor and make sure your unconscious bias does not stop you from being"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 679756,
          "dDurationMs": 2880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "in action. If you experience unfairness,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 682796,
          "dDurationMs": 3000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "use it as an opportunity to help someone else out."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 686756,
          "dDurationMs": 4240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Share what you’ve learned"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 690996,
          "dDurationMs": 3320,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Family, colleagues. Conversations add up."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 694876,
          "dDurationMs": 4160,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Support those you've helped and help them support others."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 699396,
          "dDurationMs": 5120,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "Communities grow resilient when people look out for one another."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 706196,
          "dDurationMs": 4880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "You don't need permission or a special title."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 712156,
          "dDurationMs": 1720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "You just need to start."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 714956,
          "dDurationMs": 2720,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "And finally, remember this."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 718036,
          "dDurationMs": 5520,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "You do not have to win over 100% of people"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 723836,
          "dDurationMs": 1560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "to the Di cause,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 726916,
          "dDurationMs": 1560,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "or even half."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 729516,
          "dDurationMs": 2600,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "According to researchers at Harvard,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 732116,
          "dDurationMs": 6240,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "it only takes mobilizing just 3.5%"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tStartMs": 738356,
          "dDurationMs": 3360,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "of people to bring about lasting change."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 743116,
          "dDurationMs": 1000,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "That's all."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cues": [
        {
          "tStartMs": 744956,
          "dDurationMs": 3880,
          "segs": [
            {
              "utf8": "So let's do this Di thing together."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
